      "options": {
        "content": "## NMT Overview\nThis dashboard combines raw `telephon` metrics, RabbitMQ queue depth, reliable derived metrics, and clearly labeled **Approx** formula metrics.\n\nFast path = NMT. `approx_score_nmt_seconds` is the unweighted NMT base score before router-side `p_llm` weighting. `q.out_gateway` is not used as a main formula input. Downstream context here is `q.nmt_to_llm`.",
